1) On wp-local machine 
   - make sure the user Adam exists
   - backup db
   - run rebaselinks on the wp-content folder
   - git commit and push

2) On live
   - ftp the wp-content folder onto live
   - empty all db tables except user and usermeta using WP-DP-admin (sp)
   - take the sql backup and paste it in the run-sql window and run
   - re-activate the plugins and in the theme, save all settings
   